com.example.SDLA

Class Question

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.SDLA.Question
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Question
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Custom data class to represent a quiz question. A question, assigned to a subject and a difficulty level , consists of a question and three options (one answer), of when it was made.
